                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8911" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0581</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1203 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">芯龙半导体技术公司人力资源管理的演变历程</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Evolution of Human Resource Management in Xinlong Semiconductor Technology Company</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王振源，任玉文，王岩，沈丽琼，刘静茹，刘强雨</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华东师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海芯龙半导体技术股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源管理阶段；管理思潮；企业战略；芯龙技术</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Human resource management stage; Management ideology; Corporate strategy; Xinlong Technology</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例聚焦芯龙技术这一芯片科创企业，在引入芯片行业背景和芯龙技术创业故事后，重点讲述芯龙技术各阶段人力资源管理的问题和举措，并引导学生对其各人力资源管理阶段的特点进行归纳。在思考各人力资源管理阶段特点出现底层原因的基础上，将管理思潮的演进与之对应，学习和熟悉管理思潮演进下各管理理论的基本观点，从而深刻理解管理思潮下各理论的相关观点对于人力资源管理阶段演变的重要作用。本案例通过剖析芯龙技术人力资源管理的发展演变，旨在帮助学生深入掌握人力资源管理各阶段特征，并进一步理解出现这些变化的底层管理思潮演变的推动作用，引导学生对如何因时而变，构建科学高效的企业人力资源管理体系进行思考，同时为企业人力资源管理提供实践指导。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case focuses on Xinlong Technology, a chip science and technology innovation enterprise. After introducing the background of the chip industry and the entrepreneurial story of, we focus on discussing the problems and measures of human resource management in each stage of Xinlong Technology, and guide students to summarize the features. On the basis of considering the underlying reasons for the features of various stages of human resource management, corresponding to the evolution of management trends, we study the viewpoints of various management theories under the evolution of management trends to understand the important role of relevant viewpoints of various theories under management trends. This case analyzes the development and evolution of human resource management at Xinlong Technology, aiming to help students understand the features of each stage of human resource management, and further understand the driving role of the evolution of underlying management trends that have undergone these changes. It guides students to think about how to build a scientific human resource management system that changes with the times, and provides practical guidance for enterprise human resource management.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》、《战略人力资源管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源管理阶段；管理思潮；人力资源战略与企业战略匹配；战略人力资源管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-11</td>
                            </tr>
